OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud retreating to western
OL,6,Fcoasts during the morning, where it
OL,7,Fmay linger throughout Tuesday.
OL,8,FElsewhere, a very warm day with spells
OL,9,Fof strong sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome low cloud covers the
OL,12,Fnorth coast of Cornwall. Otherwise a
OL,13,Fclear night to come with light winds.
OL,14,FMist and fog developing in prone spots
OL,15,Fin the southwest. Feeling mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAny mist and fog will lift
OL,18,Fquickly, leaving a bright and sunny
OL,19,Fday for all. Feeling hot in the strong
OL,20,Fsunshine, especially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
